data.name: NASAL OXYGEN CANNULA
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC, 100% DEHP-FREE PVC and Silicone

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC, DEHP-FREE PVC and Silicone
- Adjustable Nose Whole Distance
- Transparent and Transparent/Green Color
- Adult, Paediatric, Infant and Neonate
- Straight and Curved Prong

## PERFORMANCE
- High Tube Memory kink-resistant
- Smooth surface
